        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东吴下书人求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启主公：东吴下书人求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传你进去，你要小心了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩见关将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你奉何人所差？"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉鲁大夫所差，有书信呈上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（兵卒呈书信。〖牌子〗。关羽看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你对鲁大夫言道：修书不及，照书行事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（兵卒下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来鲁肃前来，邀请某过江饮宴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁肃约请父亲饮宴，断无好意，父亲不可前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某若不去，岂不被东吴耻笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然如此，父亲岂可以万金之躯，轻入虎穴？倘有差池，怎能对得皇伯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想某家出兵多年，纵横天下，岂惧那东吴小辈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父亲一定前去，必须多带人马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只用大船一只，挑选关西大汉数名，在船中服役。周仓一人跟随。船上插红旗\n一面，再备白旗一面，暗藏船中。吾儿准备战船二十只，领精兵一千名，在江\n心伺候。倘若东吴有诈，那时将白旗摆动，吾儿带兵急速接应，料无妨碍也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关平儿随为父出兵多年，尚不深悉用兵之道。站立一旁，听为父教训。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为将帅者，必须要通晓天文，深明地理，熟读兵书，通习战策。统兵出战，更\n须足智多谋。治兵以纪律为先，临阵以精细为上。统率将士，体恤人心，宽以\n济猛，猛以济宽；有功则赏，有过者罚。交锋之际，量自己之强弱，查敌人之\n虚实。有道是：“知彼知己，百战百胜。”乘其未至，攻其不备。运筹帷幄之\n中，决胜千里之外。诈败不可紧追，得胜不可妄进。安营扎寨，靠山近水。深\n林防埋伏，苇塘防火攻。战无不胜，攻无不取。此所谓行军之诀也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "用兵之道须谨慎，\n临阵交锋要小心。\n得胜成功休逞能。\n靠山近水扎大营。\n旗开得胜把功成。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、关平、周仓同下。）"
        }
      ],
