    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "今日里饮酒在临江亭上",
        "关羽",
        "叫人来看大杯把酒献上",
        "吴将",
        "周仓",
        "周泰",
        "想当年破黄巾东除西荡",
        "数十载动干戈未离马上",
        "甘宁",
        "盖世功劳人人钦仰",
        "陈武",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、鲁肃、甘宁、关羽、周仓同上，鲁肃、关羽同坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯驾到，肃，未曾远迎，望祈恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某家久未致侯，大夫恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫见召，足见多情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宴齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摆宴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（细吹打。四龙套同送酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯请酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。鲁肃、关羽同饮酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯海量，今日还须多饮数杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叨扰了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在吴江与大夫共饮琼浆，\n在筵前细听我诉说衷肠：\n战吕布，杀文丑，斩却颜良。\n奉主命统大兵坐镇荆襄。\n蒙厚意备酒宴甚实叨光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "想当年破黄巾东除西荡、数十载动干戈未离马上、今日里饮酒在临江亭上、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "君侯说话太谦让，\n鲁肃言来细听端详：\n灭黄巾破吕布天下名扬。\n蒙大驾肯惠临东吴有光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "想当年破黄巾东除西荡、数十载动干戈未离马上、今日里饮酒在临江亭上、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯辱临，定要畅饮一回。想当年君侯辞曹以后，过五关，斩六将，单骑千里\n之时，可能说与肃一听否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "盖世功劳人人钦仰、叫人来看大杯把酒献上、关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫若不嫌絮烦，待某手舞足蹈，细讲一番。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听道："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹腔慢板） 想当年曹营多安享，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为寻兄长出许昌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沿途关口动刀枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩福、王植马前亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卞喜被某剑劈在庙廊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀砍秦琪丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擂鼓三通斩蔡阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯武艺无敌，可谓是天神也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹腔慢板） 似这等神勇无人敢挡，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "博得美名天下扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯，鲁肃有一言，不知当讲不当讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何金言，当面领教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因当年皇叔，借去我国荆州，屯军养马。那时曾经言道：日后得了西川，即\n将荆州交还我主。前次我国先生诸葛瑾曾到西川，奉皇叔之命，领取荆州。君\n侯再三不与，不只是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日饮宴，乃是朋友人情，军国大事，不须提起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……还要君侯裁夺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鸣小锣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！这是什么响亮？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是我的宝刀啸声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是君侯刀啸？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知这刀，几年一啸？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此刀，自某在范阳桃园结拜以来，即有此刀。至今数十余年。连今日，只啸三\n次。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知刀啸主何吉凶？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不过是杀人而已。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何以见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第一次刀啸，应在斩颜良诛文丑；第二次刀啸，应在过五关斩六将；今日刀啸，\n只恐怕要应在大夫的身上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃吓倒，四龙套同扶鲁肃起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周仓，看刀来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽持酒接刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀吓，青龙刀！想你随某出兵多年，也不知斩了多少上将。今日鲁大夫设宴相\n邀，在临江亭上饮酒，你也要饮得一杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽泼酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （吹腔慢板） 青龙偃月白光凝，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "能征惯战血染红。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯再饮几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒已够了，某家要告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽接刀拉鲁肃。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （吹腔慢板） 多蒙大夫情意厚，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "醉酒饱德意悠悠。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一醉便能解千愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搭了扶手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫，某深感盛情，多谢了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（开船。关羽、周仓同下。陈武、周泰、甘宁、吴将同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武、周泰、甘宁、吴将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫为何将关公放走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位将军吓，看那关公。虽然言语和悦，他面带杀气，他提刀在手。我鲁肃若\n一言动手，他必先杀我鲁肃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武、周泰、甘宁、吴将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计岂不是又不成了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武、周泰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不若我等驾起船只，领兵赶上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那江心之内，有许多兵船，定是他国接应。我等万万不可前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计既已成画饼，只好另作良图便了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用尽千般计，仍旧一场空。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
